msgstr "మీకు ఇప్పటికే ఒక ఖాతా ఉందా?"

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/signup_done.html:6
msgid "Confirmation Sent"
msgstr "నిర్ధారణ పంపబడింది"

#: suchar_overflow/templates/registration/signup_done.html:25
msgid ""
"We have sent you an email to confirm your registration. Please check your "
